<item>
            <title>[HBASE-755] Add a method to retrieve the size and other information of a table</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-755</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;it would be good to have a method to obtain the size of a table - the total bytes of all HStore files in HDFS( hdfs://xxx/table name/column name/xxx/data), &lt;br/&gt;
and maybe other information like the number of splits etc.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i think it&apos;s a simple but (probably) important aspect to evaluate a table.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
